'''天主教安蒂戈尼什教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Antigonicensis}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]]一個[[天主教|天主教]][[教區|教區]]，位於[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]東北部，包括[[布雷頓角島|布雷頓角島]]。教區屬[[天主教哈利法克斯-雅茅斯總教區|哈利法克斯-雅茅斯總教區]]，2004年時教友有129,905人、123個堂區和127名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-de|韋恩·若瑟·柯克帕特里克|Wayne Joseph Kirkpatrick}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 18.12.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/18/191218b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-12-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218134430/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/18/191218b.html |archivedate=2019-12-18 |language=en |date=2019-12-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{link-en|貝恩·若瑟·鄧恩|Brian Joseph Dunn}}於2009年接替了因被控收藏[[兒童色情|兒童色情]]物品而辭職的{{link-en|雷蒙·萊希|Raymond Lahey}}。<ref name="porn">{{cite news|publisher=明報|title=前主教被控藏兒童色情物品　教宗委斯省新主教|url=http://www.mingpaotor.com/htm/News/20091122/tdh1.htm|date=2009-11-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091127095946/http://www.mingpaotor.com/htm/News/20091122/tdh1.htm|archivedate=2009-11-27|accessdate=2009-12-14}}</ref>

1844年9月22日自哈利法克斯教區析出，原來的教座設於[[亞力夏特|亞力夏特]]。1886年遷至[[安蒂戈尼什|安蒂戈尼什]]。<ref name="history">{{cite news |publisher=Diocese of Antigonish |title=History of The Diocese |url=http://www.antigonishdiocese.com/history.htm |accessdate=2009-12-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606035945/http://www.antigonishdiocese.com/history.htm |archivedate=2009-06-06 }}</ref>

